name: geojsonio.py
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.0.2" %}

package:
    name: geojsonio.py
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: geojsonio-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/g/geojsonio/geojsonio-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    md5: e75b0ec0786d456dc630f93874106bfd

build:
    number: 0
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt
    entry_points:
        - geojsonio = geojsonio:main


requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
    run:
        - python
        - github3.py
        - six

test:
    imports:
        - geojsonio
    commands:
        - geojsonio --help

about:
    home: https://github.com/jwass/geojsonio.py
    license: BSD-3-Clause
    summary: geojsonio CLI - Python.

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
